ontology:
@prefix : <http://example.com/sanctions#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

### Classes
:SanctionedEntity a owl:Class .
:SanctioningAuthority a owl:Class .
:Sanction a owl:Class .

### Object Properties
:hasSanctioningAuthority a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :SanctionedEntity ;
    rdfs:range :SanctioningAuthority .
:hasSanction a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :SanctionedEntity ;
    rdfs:range :Sanction .

### Datatype Properties
:CNPJCPF a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :SanctionedEntity ;
    rdfs:range xsd:string .
:name a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :SanctionedEntity ;
    rdfs:range xsd:string .
:state a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :SanctionedEntity ;
    rdfs:range xsd:string .
:sanctionCategory a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :Sanction ;
    rdfs:range xsd:string .
:initialDate a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :Sanction ;
    rdfs:range xsd:date .
:finalDate a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :Sanction ;
    rdfs:range xsd:date .
:publicationDate a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :Sanction ;
    rdfs:range xsd:string .
:fineValue a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :Sanction ;
    rdfs:range xsd:integer .
:quantity a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:domain :Sanction ;
    rdfs:range xsd:float .

### Hierarchical Relationships
:SanctionedEntity rdfs:subClassOf :Sanction .
:SanctioningAuthority rdfs:subClassOf :Sanction .
